Reservoir Capital Partners
Reservoir Capital Partners, L.P. was formed to capitalize on exceptional, non-recurring investment opportunities frequently found in areas experiencing fundamental change and/or scarcity of capital. The fund makes investments both directly and by partnering with world-class management teams or specialists. In October 1999, Reservoir Capital Partners closed at a total capitalization of $447 million.
Reservoir Capital Group is a privately-held investment firm with an opportunistic hybrid investment approach.

