Company Description


Reservoir Capital Group LLC provides investment advisory services. The firm invests directly in both public and private markets as well as in partnership with investment teams. It also provides risk and reward profiles, superior economics and proprietary deal flow. The company was founded by Daniel Hennelly Stern, Craig Allen Huff and Gregg Matthew Zeitlin in 1998 and is headquartered in New York, NY.




