Intrepid Aviation Ltd.

                                    Intrepid Aviation Ltd. operates through acquiring and leasing of passenger aircrafts. The company was founded on February 5, 2013 and is headquartered in Stamford, CT.                                





 Details Hidden



C12 Energy LLC

                                    C12 Energy LLC develops carbon sequestration technology. Its primary business involves rehabilitating mature fields through gas injection. The firm's technologies separate emissions streams and inject those emissions into geological formations for storage. It also develops, owns, and operates projects that manage industrial carbon dioxide in subsurface geologic structures for enhanced oil recovery and long-term storage. The company was founded by Charles M. Brankman, Justin Dawe and Kurt Zenz House in 2008 and is headquartered in Berkeley, CA.                                





