Energoremont Holding AD

                                     •  Other Business & Consulting Services                                                                             •  Sofia, SC                                                                    

                                    Energoremont Holding AD engages in the provision of repair and construction. Its activities include rehabilitation, reconstruction, modernization and construction of power systems in thermal power plants, heating power plants, water power plants and nuclear power Plants, facilities in gas-petroleum, chemical and mine industry and transport infrastructure. It also involved in the design, production, delivery, construction and installation of power equipment and metal structures, as well as control and determination of the resource of the metals; as well as maintenance. The company was founded in 1969 and is headquartered in Sofia, Bulgaria.
                                






